{"tid":2017251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"電子錢包現保安漏洞，PayMe過數，第三者可「截糊」擸錢","createTime":"2020-05-15T03:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T03:52:12.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9749e90c2add9faf2a3485cb3d9f9bf5195e38ff","tid":2017251,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎陰霾下，市民為避疫足不出戶轉為網上購物，令電子錢包交易額大增，卻疑衍生保安漏洞。有消費者近日以PayMe轉賬6,000元給朋友，卻意外發現該筆款項竟可透過PayLink（付款超連結）遭第三者「截糊」取走，批評是一大漏洞，擔心其他用戶因此蒙受損失，「我覺得PayMe係絕對需要負責任」。本報測試發現，另一流行電子錢包支付寶亦有相同問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200515/C3HDWPASYXCA7O2O6KPB4HQNCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FC3HDWPASYXCA7O2O6KPB4HQNCQ%2F&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=0cdd66ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FC3HDWPASYXCA7O2O6KPB4HQNCQ%2F&h=79b8edf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200515/C3HDWPASYXCA7O2O6KPB4HQNCQ/</a>"}]}